data.description: Welcome home to this charming 3-bedroom haven, where comfort meets elegance. Unwind in the embrace of 2 full restrooms, your private retreat after a long day. Step into the heart of the home, where the chef’s haven awaits with a gas stove ready to turn your culinary dreams into reality.    Sip your morning coffee on the spacious front porch, soaking in the tranquility of this quiet neighborhood. Host intimate gatherings or simply bask in serenity on the patio deck, adorned with an inviting awning for those lazy afternoons.    But that’s not all – practicality meets preparedness with a Generac generator, ensuring peace of mind in any weather. This cozy abode is not just a house; it’s a sanctuary waiting to embrace its next chapter. Welcome to a home that whispers “you belong here.”
